data.description: Active Under Contract - Accepting Back Up Offers  -  Step into modern elegance with this beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 2-bath home. Every detail has been carefully curated to blend contemporary style with comfort. The open-concept living space welcomes you with abundant natural light, highlighting the sleek finishes and hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, wine refrigerator and a huge, granite covered island - perfect for culinary adventures or casual gatherings. Retreat to the spacious sized bedrooms; each designed for relaxation and privacy. Newly remodeled bathrooms offer a touch of luxury to your daily routine.  The primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet and a double walk-in shower!    The Villages at Avalon has their own clubhouse complete with a large community pool and fitness room.  Low quarterly HOA too.  With a prime location to 589/Veterans Expressway (less than 5 minutes away), your commute will be a breeze.  This home is a harmonious blend of sophistication and practicality--a haven for modern living.  Be sure to check out the 3D virtual walk thru for a true feeling for the layout of this home.
